race.comment: HARD SOLO (11) was last seen in the G2 Karrakatta Plate where she found it a touch hot, but her earlier form stacked up well. A recent trial should have her forward enough. Could simply outclass them. BUSY FINGERS (2) showed great signs in his debut prep, including a close placing at Albany. Back from a good break with two solid trials under the belt and drawn to get the run of the race. Major player. CHINESE DENTIST (4) hit the line nicely when resuming here and will be fitter for that. Genuine chance if he gets tempo. SHE'SATROOPER (10) stuck on solidly into midfield when resuming off a long break here. Can improve sharply with blinkers going on. BIG BOPPER (3) showed early dash fresh and can give cheek again if he crosses cleanly.
